snippet.title: Angry Birds: Pigs Out!
snippet.description: Angry Birds: Pigs Out! Physics puzzle. Try to erase the green pigs from each level. Cut ropes and wood to get it done.

snippet.title: Kamikaze Pigs
snippet.description: Kamikaze Pigs Action game. Destroy the pigs in the war and earn enough stars to upgrade your gear.

snippet.title: Pig On The Rocket
snippet.description: Pig On The Rocket Fly through the skies on your rocket, collect fruit and fuel but avoid the bird named Flappy.

snippet.title: Pig Wars
snippet.description: Pig Wars Blow up as many enemies as possible and don't let them to destroy you.

snippet.title: Clay Pigeon Shooter
snippet.description: Clay Pigeon Shooter Shoot the moving targets quickly and accurately from both the directions.

snippet.title: Super 3D Pig Feeder
snippet.description: Super 3D Pig Feeder 3D shooting game in the classic DOOM setup. Bring all pigs asleep and get to the end of each level.

snippet.title: Pig Detective
snippet.description: Pig Detective Point & click puzzle adventure. Find and catch the criminal in this funny city where you can do anything.

snippet.title: Pigdream
snippet.description: Pigdream Platform adventure. Save the ancient manuscripts from destruction and try to defeat the bosses.

snippet.title: Pigs Can Fly
snippet.description: Pigs Can Fly Physics puzzle game. Try to get the pig to the potion by moving objects in different timelines.

snippet.title: Piggy Wiggy
snippet.description: Piggy Wiggy Physics puzzle. Your mission is to get the pigs to the acorns using ropes to get them there.
